  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.intro.header": "认识烈焰人附魔室",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.intro.text_1": "这是一个烈焰人附魔室，它的功能类似于附魔台",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.intro.text_2": "通入液态经验让其开始工作",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.intro.text_3": "在开始附魔之前，你需要通过仪表盘设置附魔等级（附魔机制的工作等级，非产出附魔本身的等级）。原版附魔台的附魔等级上限为30",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.intro.text_4": "仪表盘同时也是过滤插槽。持有物品右键过滤插槽可以将物品设置为模板物品，这就是模板附魔模式。",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.intro.text_5": "在模板附魔模式下，烈焰人附魔室可对附魔模板进行附魔，且只会生成可出现在模板物品上的附魔。",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.header": "超越附魔时间!",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.text_1": "你也许注意到了，附魔室中的烈焰人有两个“胃”。要不试试给它吃一点附魔蛋糕？",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.text_2": "哇哦，它正在超级燃烧！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.text_3": "现在，它已准备好做一些了不起的事了！可设置的附魔等级获得了极大提升！宝藏附魔将出现！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.text_4": "相信我，你会需要这个的",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.text_5": "超越附魔会招致雷击",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.text_6": "你可以在烈焰人附魔室正上方放置方块来躲避雷击，但诅咒附魔将会出现",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_enchanter.super_enchant.text_7": "你啥都不想做？也成",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.intro.header": "认识烈焰人锻造室",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.intro.text_1": "这是一个烈焰人锻造室，它的功能类似于铁砧",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.intro.text_2": "通入液态经验让其开始工作",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.intro.text_3": "烈焰人锻造室能够合并同种物品的附魔，就像在铁砧上那样，并且不再有“累积惩罚”",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.intro.text_4": "烈焰人锻造室还能合并附魔模板",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.intro.text_5": "最重要的是，烈焰人锻造室能够将附魔模板应用到物品上！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.intro.text_6": "而且，烈焰人锻造室还能将装备，附魔书和附魔模板上的附魔剥离到空白的附魔模板上",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.header": "超越附魔时间!",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_1": "你也许注意到了，锻造室中的烈焰人有两个“胃”。要不要喂它一点附魔蛋糕吃？",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_2": "看！超级燃烧状态的烈焰人！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_3": "现在，它已准备好做一些令人着迷的事了！突破附魔等级上限！合并冲突附魔！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_4": "顺带一提，超越附魔模板只能在这个状态下被应用和处理",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_5": "别忘了放一根避雷针，你会需要的",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_6": "超越附魔会招致雷击",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_7": "你可以在烈焰人锻造室正上方放置方块来躲避雷击，但“累积惩罚”将会出现",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.blaze_forger.super_enchant.text_8": "你不喜欢天花板和避雷针？好吧",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.advance.header": "你也许会感兴趣的事",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.advance.text_1": "在准备和附魔打交道之前，你需要了解这么几件事",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.advance.text_2": "经验块不再是纯粹的装饰性和存储型方块，你之后会需要用到它",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.advance.text_3": "这是超越经验块，制作超越附魔模板需要它",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.advance.text_4": "烈焰人附魔室",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.advance.text_5": "烈焰人锻造室",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.advance.text_6": "超越附魔能让你超越极限！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.header": "了解如何处理和运用经验",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_1": "这是一罐液态经验，它将会是经验在加工过程中最常见的形态",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_10": "如果你需要将液态经验装回容器物品中，可以使用注液器",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_11": "别担心，泄露的液态经验会转化成经验球",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_2": "将你携带的经验转化为流体形式，需要这两个元件",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_3": "流体舱口可以直接存取物品中的经验",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_4": "经验舱口可以直接存取玩家携带的经验",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_5": "自动化是机械动力不可或缺的一部分，对吧？",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_6": "你可以使用分液池来将物品中的液态经验倒出",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_7": "你还可以使用动力砂轮将物品，比如经验颗粒，粉碎为液态经验",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_8": "粉碎轮现在有了新机制：被粉碎轮碾死的生物有小概率掉落经验颗粒",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.intro.text_9": "机械手也有了新机制：机械手杀死生物后会掉落经验颗粒",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.prepare_for_super_enchant.header": "准备超越附魔的材料",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.prepare_for_super_enchant.text_1": "第一种材料是超越经验块，它能被加工成超越附魔模板。这需要经验块",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.prepare_for_super_enchant.text_2": "雷击！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience.prepare_for_super_enchant.text_3": "第二种材料是附魔蛋糕，它有着“超经验”的作用，用于支持烈焰人的超级燃烧模式。烈焰人会爱死这种小零食的",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.header": "认识经验舱口",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.text_1": "使用方式非常简单。右键舱口存储经验……",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.text_2": "……蹲下右键舱口取出经验。",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.text_3": "舱口侧面有一个过滤插槽和仪表盘。通过仪表盘，你可以在仪表盘上设置每次存取经验的上限",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.text_4": "过滤插槽则用来处理其他模组的经验流体",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.text_5": "打个比方，我们假设青色染料是来自其他模组的经验流体……",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.text_6": "……并且将过滤插槽设置为青色燃料桶",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.experience_hatch.intro.text_7": "现在，你可以直接将经验值存取为“青色经验”了！",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.extra.header": "动力砂轮，不只是砂轮",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.extra.text_1": "动力砂轮不仅有砂轮的全部功能……",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.extra.text_2": "...而且还有砂纸的功能",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.extra.text_3": "你可以直接手持物品使用动力砂轮。绝对安全不伤手，嘿嘿",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.intro.header": "认识动力砂轮",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.intro.text_1": "要使用动力砂轮，你需要一个分液池",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.intro.text_2": "这是一个砂轮分液池。你还需要另外一个动力砂轮才能使用它",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.mechanical_grindstone.intro.text_3": "物品形式的经验会被动力砂轮粉碎为液体形式",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.printer.intro.header": "认识打印机",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.printer.intro.text_1": "这是一台打印机",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.printer.intro.text_2": "在你开始使用之前，你需要将你想打印的东西设置在过滤插槽上……",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.printer.intro.text_3": "……并且通入对应的液体",
  "create_enchantment_industry.ponder.printer.intro.text_4": "你可以随时使用JEI等配方查询模组来查看打印配方",
